{
  "stem": "19969.7",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 141.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So the-- some of the post war things that I found out are quite interesting, but particularly this file that I have here where the inspector general-- I didn't realize that he'd counted the bullet holes in that wall and he has each one marked where those 11 that I know of where killed there.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it's-- I have studied, I've read everything I could find on it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some of the books are in foreign tongue that I can't read.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They've been given to me by-- another thing that I did not realize was the-- the large-- to the-- to the extent to which the French cooperated with the Germans in concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's been downplayed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But there were concentration camps in France that were manned by Frenchmen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All the-- the overseers were Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the French-- the Vichy government cooperated fully in rounding up the Jews in France.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And of course, the French today are still after some of the-- I mean, you got a trial of various people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I have had an opportunity to talk to a great number of people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I have traveled in various states-- Texas, Oklahoma, Wyoming, Utah, California-- and spoken to various groups.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "One thing I found out last year-- I was in San Antonio, Texas-- I met a professor, an American professor, who was teaching at Emory University in Atlanta.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he said, general, I bet-- he said, I bet you don't know that there was one country that refused to cooperate with Hitler.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I said, no, I never heard of that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Well, it turned out this professor was from Bulgaria.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Now, Bulgaria was an Axis partner, all of Balkan states were.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
